    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">БУЙРУҚ</span></p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Буйруқ қабул қилинган сана</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Буйруқ рақами</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#4}Буйруқ қабул қилинган жой</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">Тўлиқсиз</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">иш куни билан ишга қабул қилиш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Меҳнат кодексининг 186-моддасига мувофиқ ходимга тўлиқсиз иш вақти белгиланиши мумкин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Меҳнат шартномаси тарафларининг келишувига кўра ходимга ишга қабул қилиш чоғида ва кейинчалик тўлиқсиз иш вақти (тўлиқсиз иш куни (смена) ва (ёки) тўлиқсиз иш ҳафтаси, шу жумладан иш кунини қисмларга бўлган ҳолда) белгиланиши мумкин. Тўлиқсиз иш вақти ҳам муддати чекланмаган ҳолда, ҳам меҳнат шартномаси тарафлари келишган ҳар қандай муддатга белгиланиши мумкин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Меҳнат кодексининг 127, 186-моддаларига мувофиқ, </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">БУЮРАМАН</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">1. </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#6}Ходимнинг фамилияси, исми, отасининг исм</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> – </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#7}Ходим қабул қилинаётган лавозим</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">лигига тўлиқсиз иш куни билан штатлар жадвалига мувофиқ, </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#8}Ходим ишга қабул қилинадиган сана</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">дан ишга қабул қилинсин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> Иш соати </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#9}Иш соатининг бошланиши</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">дан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#10}Иш соатининг тугаши</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">гача этиб белгилансин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> Бухгалтерия бўлимига: ходим </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#6}Ходимнинг фамилияси, исми, отасининг исм</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">га тегишли тўловлар амалдаги қонунчилик ҳужжатларида белгиланган тартибда амалга оширилсин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.133333333333px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.133333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">Асос: </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Меҳнат кодексининг 127, 186-моддалари, </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; color: #000000;\">{#6}Ходимнинг фамилияси, исми, отасининг исм</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000;\">билан тузилган меҳнат шартномаси.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#11}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг лавозими</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">_______________</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#12}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"